title: Qatar Repo Rate
description: Qatar Repo Rate was at 4.75 percent on Thursday November 10. Reverse Repo Rate in Qatar averaged 3.82 percent from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 6.65 percent in July of 2000 and a record low of 1 percent in March of 2020. This page provides - Qatar Reverse Repo Rate- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Qatar Central Bank
